'''Diane''' is a woman who sustained a minor injury during the Five and Dime fire.

==History==
Diane was at the Rogers' Five and Dime when a kid set off some fireworks indoors. As they left the building, Diane fell and her husband tripped over her. She was seen at the triage area outside.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
She is married.
